    <h1>Pre-Trial Summons - Notice of Intent to Pursue Legal Action</h1>

    <p>Dear {{ $json.KontrahentNazwa }},</p>

    <p><strong>RE: OVERDUE INVOICE - FORMAL NOTICE OF INTENT TO COMMENCE LEGAL PROCEEDINGS</strong></p>

