=<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 650px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
    .header {
      border-bottom: 3px solid #1a237e; /* Navy blue for formal court notice */
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .company-name {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #1a237e;
      margin: 0 0 5px 0;
    }
    .company-tagline {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666666;
      margin: 0;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #c62828;
      font-size: 22px;
      margin: 0 0 20px 0;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .urgent-notice {
      background-color: #ffebee;
      border-left: 4px solid #c62828;
      padding: 15px 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
    .urgent-notice p {
      margin: 5px 0;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #c62828;
    }
    .case-details {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    }
    .case-details table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }
    .case-details td {
      padding: 8px 0;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .case-details td:first-child {
      color: #666666;
      width: 45%;
    }
    .case-details td:last-child {
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: right;
    }
    .legal-warning {
      background-color: #fff3cd;
      border: 2px solid #ff6f00;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .legal-warning h2 {
      color: #c62828;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin: 0 0 15px 0;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .deadline-box {
      background-color: #1a237e; /* Navy for the finality of court */
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
    .deadline-box h2 {
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
      font-size: 20px;
    }
    .deadline-date {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #666666;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .formal-signature {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <p class="company-name">{{$('Your Company Details').first().json['Company Name']}}</p>
      <p class="company-tagline">Legal Department - Litigation Division</p>
    </div>

    <h1>FORMAL COURT SUMMONS & NOTICE OF LITIGATION</h1>

    <p>Dear {{ $json.KontrahentNazwa }},</p>

    <p><strong>RE: FINAL NOTICE PRIOR TO JUDICIAL ENFORCEMENT - CASE REF: {{$json['FakturaId']}}</strong></p>

    <div class="urgent-notice">
      <p>STATUS: LEGAL PROCEEDINGS FORMALLY INITIATED</p>
      <p>This is your final administrative opportunity to prevent a court hearing.</p>
    </div>

    <p>You are hereby notified that <strong>{{$('Your Company Details').first().json['Company Name']}}</strong> has moved your account to active litigation. A petition for the recovery of debt has been prepared for filing against you for the following outstanding balance:</p>

    <div class="case-details">
      <table>
        <tr>
          <td>Claim Reference:</td>
          <td>LIT-{{$json['FakturaId']}}-{{$now.format('yyyy')}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Associated Invoice:</td>
          <td>{{$json['PelnyNumer']}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Principal Amount:</td>
          <td>{{$json.Brutto}} {{ $json.Waluta }}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Current Interest & Fees:</td>
          <td style="color: #c62828;">+ Statutory Charges Accruing</td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="border-top: 2px solid #dddddd;">
          <td style="padding-top: 15px; font-weight: bold;">TOTAL CLAIM VALUE:</td>
          <td style="padding-top: 15px; font-size: 20px; color: #1a237e;">{{$json.Brutto}} {{ $json.Waluta }}*</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <p style="font-size: 11px; margin-top: 10px;">*Excluding future court costs and bailiff execution fees.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-warning">
      <h2>Notice of Judicial Action</h2>
      <p>Upon the expiration of the deadline below, the following actions will proceed without further warning:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Filing of Lawsuit:</strong> Formal entry of the claim into the civil court system.</li>
        <li><strong>Public Record:</strong> The litigation will be registered against your credit profile, affecting future financing.</li>
        <li><strong>Asset Attachment:</strong> Application for the seizure of bank accounts or property to satisfy the debt.</li>
        <li><strong>Additional Costs:</strong> You will be held liable for all legal fees, process server costs, and court levies.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="deadline-box">
      <h2>FINAL SETTLEMENT DEADLINE</h2>
      <p class="deadline-date">{{$now.plus(( $('Configuration').first().json['Z days after due date'] - $('Configuration').first().json['Y days after due date'] ), 'days').format('MMMM dd, yyyy')}}</p>
      <p>All legal actions will be stayed ONLY if full payment is confirmed before this date.</p>
    </div>

    <p><strong>TO STOP LEGAL PROCEEDINGS:</strong> You must immediately transfer the total amount due to the account details provided below and provide a PDF confirmation to our legal department.</p>

    <div style="background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 25px 0; border-left: 4px solid #1a237e;">
      <p style="margin-top: 0;"><strong>Bank Name:</strong> {{$('Your Company Details').first().json['Bank Name']}}</p>
      <p><strong>Account Number:</strong> {{$('Your Company Details').first().json['Bank Account Number']}}</p>
      <p><strong>SWIFT/BIC:</strong> {{$('Your Company Details').first().json['Swift Code']}}</p>
      <p><strong>Reference:</strong> CASE-{{$json['PelnyNumer']}}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="formal-signature">
      <p>
        Respectfully,<br><br>
        <strong>Litigation & Recovery Department</strong><br>
        {{$('Your Company Details').first().json['Company Name']}}<br>
        {{$('Your Company Details').first().json['Email']}}
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #999999;">
        <strong>Date of Issue:</strong> {{$now.format('MMMM dd, yyyy')}}
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p><strong>{{$('Your Company Details').first().json['Company Name']}}</strong></p>
      <p>This is an official communication. Failure to respond has serious legal consequences.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
